\newlabel{fig:net}{{3}{5}{Network topology. OptiTrack reaches the robot LAN over Ethernet via the ROS host and Wi-Fi access point; VRPN poses ride a secondary Wi-Fi link. The Jetson manages the RDK~X3 over SSH (control plane) and exchanges topics over DDS (data plane), and bridges the Tello over its proprietary UDP SDK}{figure.3}{}}
