\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4}{\ignorespaces Mission orchestrator state machine. Stages advance left-to-right, top-to-bottom (01--06 then 07--12). The map-quality classifier (04.c) is the sole branch: \textsc  {pass} routes the planner to \texttt  {/drone/map} with a goal pose; \textsc  {fail} publishes a border-template map and arms the frontier-exploration fallback (11.b, triggered at 12.a). Any sub-stage failure transitions to the ABORT sink, which lands the drone before tearing down.}}{6}{figure.4}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:fsm}{{4}{6}{Mission orchestrator state machine. Stages advance left-to-right, top-to-bottom (01--06 then 07--12). The map-quality classifier (04.c) is the sole branch: \textsc {pass} routes the planner to \texttt {/drone/map} with a goal pose; \textsc {fail} publishes a border-template map and arms the frontier-exploration fallback (11.b, triggered at 12.a). Any sub-stage failure transitions to the ABORT sink, which lands the drone before tearing down}{figure.4}{}}
